OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSheen sceptical of         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnon-Welsh actors in Welsh  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Froles                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Actor Michael Sheen has said that he   
OL,6, finds non-Welsh actors playing Welsh   
OL,7, characters "hard to accept".           
OL,9,FSpeaking to The Telegraph, the         
OL,10,FHollywood star addressed whether actors
OL,11,Fshould play roles they cannot          
OL,12,Fpersonally identify with.              
OL,14,FSome people have pointed out Sheen has 
OL,15,Fplayed roles such as Edinburgh-born    
OL,16,FTony Blair and David Frost from Kent.  
OL,18,FHowever, he said cast and crew of his  
OL,19,Fnew drama, Best Interests, made him    
OL,20,Fconsider this position.                
